<a href="http://www.perl.org/">Perl</a> (also see the
<a href="http://perl-begin.org/">Perl Beginners’ Site</a>).
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.python.org/">Python</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/">Ruby</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lua_%28programming_language%29">Lua</a>
</li>

<li>
<a href="http://perl6.org/">Perl 6</a> - a different language from Perl 5,
with many powerful features. Also see <a href="http://perl6maven.com/">Perl
6 Maven</a>.
</li>

</ul>

